This is a classic example of how the nature of an individual/situation is entirely different from what has been portrayed and the truth is not entirely what it seems to be. Moreso, when there's an other side to the coin...so genuine and justifiable. Therefore, it's so important to let the other person speak and clarify things before judging someone just based on some picture/video.

In this case anyway...the safety considerations are important!
No celebrity guest will want to make headlines about a tragic comedy car crash karaoke with James Corden. A camera showing James Corden driving in one scene and in the next, showing the car being towed only adds to the comedy.

Hello, my name is Edson Sampaio and I recently graduated with a doctorate in medicine in Mozambique. My dream has always been to do my medical residency in the United States, as it has one of the best medical programmes in the world; specializing in pediatric medicine, as I love working with kids and their families. In order to achieve this, I must complete 4 assignments; three computer based and 1 practical. The costs for these assignments is roughly $5,000. Additionally, I am required to complete an externship in the United States to receive a US certificate of medical experience which includes letters of recommendation. For this trip I would also need to pay for my airplane ticket and accommodation all of this rounds up to almost $5,000.

I ask for you to please share my story as to help me make my long life dream come true. Any donation is greatly appreciated
